Roadtrip anyone?😎
This German luxury RV from @volkner.mobil comes with a slide out garage that can store your hypercar! It costs $2.4 million dollars with all the luxury trimmings including a $355,000 Burmester sound system.
Throw in a @Bugatti Chiron to complete the package for $7.7 million.👀💰
